text: Zoltán Molnár (born 4 April 1961) is a Hungarian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Hungary Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Budapest
